{"tid":2208063,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"納瓦爾尼飲酒店樽裝水中毒","createTime":"2020-09-18T15:00:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T17:09:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6392b44b2ec8e212aa1e9c31e7f0599d606b7544","tid":2208063,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:00:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200918/2BJ2RX6YGJDJ5GQU32IU5ZDHV4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200918%2F2BJ2RX6YGJDJ5GQU32IU5ZDHV4%2F&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCsorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=bf2e87e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200918%2F2BJ2RX6YGJDJ5GQU32IU5ZDHV4%2F&h=5b9153ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200918/2BJ2RX6YGJDJ5GQU32IU5ZDHV4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n納瓦爾尼飲酒店樽裝水中毒<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/h1cwv5d8kteT5RiEgazGUo6CfuA=/720x538/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/74VHFKCB45HOBG3V5U7KDXR7VQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fh1cwv5d8kteT5RiEgazGUo6CfuA%3D%2F720x538%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F74VHFKCB45HOBG3V5U7KDXR7VQ.jpg&h=837b5a65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■納瓦爾尼透露在酒店遭下毒。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n因為中毒被送到德國醫治的俄羅斯反對派領袖納瓦爾尼，他的團隊昨日透露，他是透過酒店內的樽裝水中毒，而非早前外界以為的在機場喝茶出事。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/z_pv4oqbtsximlxBGqdNuvgsvLU=/1610x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5VMKHSP5ZJAEPB7HKUUP36L3QM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fz_pv4oqbtsximlxBGqdNuvgsvLU%3D%2F1610x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5VMKHSP5ZJAEPB7HKUUP36L3QM.jpg&h=735d9f8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■酒店樽裝水驗出有劇毒「諾維喬克」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n禁化武組織助查<br />\n<br />\n納瓦爾尼的Instagram賬戶前日上載了一段影片，可見其團隊得知他出事後一小時，在他曾入住的酒店、位於俄羅斯托木斯克的Xander Hotel房間內搜索，旨在「集合所有可能有用的證據，交予德國的醫生。明顯地，俄羅斯方面不會調查這案件」。最後他們戴着手套撿走了包括多支礦泉水空樽及其他物品。<br />\n<br />\n納瓦爾尼團隊留言指，兩周後，德國一間化驗所從酒店房內一支水樽驗出神經毒劑諾維喬克的痕迹。之。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，禁止化學武器組織（OPCW）昨日透露，按德國政府要求，該組織派出專家到當地，就納瓦爾尼中毒一案提供「技術援助」，從。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/美聯社"},{"pid":"4d33c63929d3d4c803853ef0638c08b1e043e88e","tid":2208063,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e58a0a80e9aa3146a2a474676aaed76780e4adb3","tid":2208063,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:14:41.000Z","msg":"蘇共玩落毒玩足咁多年"},{"pid":"314b47a3ba9cc51137647a50e098e97f0d6f19d7","tid":2208063,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e58a0a80e9aa3146a2a474676aaed76780e4adb3","tid":2208063,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:14:41.000Z","msg":"蘇共玩落毒玩足咁多年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:20:20.000Z","msg":"毒殺過好多人 但真係好高效率 又無手尾"},{"pid":"8b05e659b7de9e7d5266d745d8e1e897f2286696","tid":2208063,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"314b47a3ba9cc51137647a50e098e97f0d6f19d7","tid":2208063,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e58a0a80e9aa3146a2a474676aaed76780e4adb3","tid":2208063,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:14:41.000Z","msg":"蘇共玩落毒玩足咁多年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:20:20.000Z","msg":"毒殺過好多人 但真係好高效率 又無手尾"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T16:47:57.000Z","msg":"有冇得買？"},{"pid":"a99d73840eb89d88b502b50860ce0725ce28412f","tid":2208063,"uid":325243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T17:09:45.000Z","msg":"點解仲要留低證據？"}]}